---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<section class="bg-surface py-20 border-t border-gray-100" data-purpose="bottom-newsletter">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
    <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
      <div class="mb-6">
        <a class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-primary" href="/">CARLOSCONDOR</a>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 max-w-sm">
        <form class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2" onsubmit="event.preventDefault()">
          <input
            class="flex-1 min-w-0 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-custom border border-gray-200 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary outline-none text-sm bg-white"
            placeholder="tu@email.com"
            type="email"
          />
          <button class="w-full sm:w-auto px-5 py-2.5 bg-gray-900 text-white font-medium rounded-custom hover:bg-black transition-colors text-sm" type="submit">
            Suscribirme
          </button>
        </form>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          Algunos enlaces pueden ser de afiliación. Los precios son orientativos y pueden cambiar. Solo incluyo productos que uso, he probado o considero útiles.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div data-purpose="footer-links">
      <h4 class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-6">Navegación</h4>
      <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600 font-medium">
        <li><a class="hover:text-black transition-colors" href="/">Inicio</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-black transition-colors" href="/picks">Picks</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div data-purpose="footer-links">
      <h4 class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-6">Info</h4>
      <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600 font-medium">
        <li><a class="hover:text-black transition-colors" href="/">Sobre mí</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-black transition-colors" href="mailto:j.carloscondor@gmail.com">Contacto</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-black transition-colors" href="https://CarlosCondor.github.io/">Blog</a></li>
      </ul>
      <h4 class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mt-8 mb-6">Redes</h4>
      <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600 font-medium">
        <li><a class="hover:text-black transition-colors" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/juan-carlos-%F0%9F%91%A8%F0%9F%8F%BB%E2%80%8D%F0%9F%92%BB-delgado-jaramillo-200a0330/">LinkedIn</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-black transition-colors" href="http://github.com/carloscondor">GitHub</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<footer class="py-10 border-t border-gray-100" data-purpose="site-footer">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">© {currentYear} CarlosCondor. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Selección personal de productos recomendados.</p>
  </div>
</footer>
